<headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 22 at 6:26AM EDT  by NWS Greenville-Spartanburg</headline>
<description>...PATCHY DENSE FOG ACROSS THE NORTH CAROLINA FOOTHILLS THIS
MORNING...
Fog will be locally dense across the North Carolina foothills
this morning. Visibility may drop below one-quarter of a mile at
times, especially across the Morganton to Hickory areas and south
toward Rutherfordton. The fog should improve by 9 AM.
Those traveling should use low beams and allow for extra driving
time to get to your destination.</description>
